---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout noAds title="DMCA Policy" description="DMCA takedown policy for Resurgence Builds — how to report copyright concerns related to our Division Resurgence guides, builds, and community content.">
  <div class="container section content-width">
    <h1 class="heading-accent">DMCA Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--ink-muted);">Last updated: April 20, 2026</p>
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Respect for Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>Resurgence Builds respects the intellectual property rights of others. If you believe that content on our site infringes your copyright, please follow the procedure below.</p>

      <h2>No User-Generated Content</h2>
      <p>This website is entirely static and does not host any user-generated content, comments, or public uploads. All content is created and curated directly by the site operators. As such, we do not have a process for taking down user submissions, because there are none.</p>

      <h2>Reporting Copyright Claims</h2>
      <p>If you believe that any original article or image produced by us infringes on your copyright, please contact us at <a href="mailto:p1@cfworx.tech">p1@cfworx.tech</a> with the subject line "Copyright Inquiry".</p>

      <h2>Repeat Infringers</h2>
      <p>We will terminate access for users who are repeat infringers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
